WEBVTT

00:11:30.601 --> 00:11:36.305
Is it any wonder people in today's world
are becoming addicted so easily?

00:11:39.022 --> 00:11:40.839
Social isolation --

00:11:44.926 --> 00:11:46.076
excuse me --

00:11:47.736 --> 00:11:49.203
contributes to relapse.

00:11:49.953 --> 00:11:54.080
Studies have shown that people
who tend to avoid relapse

00:11:54.104 --> 00:11:58.903
tend to be people who have broad,
reciprocal social relationships

00:11:58.927 --> 00:12:00.956
where they can be
of service to each other,